*viewcvs-1.0_pre20050929 (03 Oct 2005)

  03 Oct 2005; Lance Albertson <ramereth@gentoo.org>
  +files/postinstall-new-en.txt, files/reconfig, viewcvs-0.9.3.ebuild,
  +viewcvs-1.0_pre20050929.ebuild:
  * New CVS snapshot with several fixes:
    * Resolved #77226 giving the option of using either
      apache1/apache2/lighttpd for cgi capable webservers
    * Resolved #106506 adding a mysql flag, and mysql-python deps for folks
      wanting to use the mysql query engine.
    * Added checks for several apps to ensure they have proper use flags
      enabled.
    * Added sql files for creating query engine tables
    * Fixed reconfig script to fix the mod_python scripts
    * Updated postinstall to include new information
  * Marked 0.9.3 stable on x86

